text: Kristian Groenintwoud (born 9 May 1973) is an Australian handball player. He competed in the men's tournament at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Australian handball players Category:Olympic handball players for Australia Category:Handball players at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Melbourne
